description: A group of marines arrive in Manaus, on orders to set off into the jungle for secret training. But their guide, Rosario Silva, dies in a mysterious way. Sergeant Oliveira can’t figure out what’s going on, and suggests Mister No and Esse-Esse should accompany the marines. The German accepts, but then disappears without a trace…
name: I Cacciatori e la Preda

description: Mister No sets off into the heart of the jungle in search of Esse-Esse. And here he has to contend with a veritable army of Marines ready for anything. In the background, some appalling experiments by a mad scientist: Doctor Miller…
name: Orrore Nella Giungla

description: The “Finger Eater”, a serial killer who is terrorizing New York, has the horrible habit of cutting off his victims’ fingers. In Manaus, instead, Mister No has four new clients (a playboy, a crime news photographer, a restaurant owner, a millionaire). But strange crimes happen in the Amazons: one of his clients could be the “Finger eater”!
name: Serial Killer

description: A highway is being constructed that will cross the Amazon jungle, and the Indios who live there have been forcefully driven out and confined (pending transferral) in a type of concentration camp run by the ruthless Capitan Herrera. Only Mister No and Father Santana defend the poor Indios but Juanito, one of the Indios, sets off a revolt…
name: La Rivolta

description: At an altitude of three hundred meters, a ramshackle village between Brazil and Venezuela. Mister No and Esse-Esse meet some strange people. They are definitely hiding something. In fact they have kidnapped the beautiful Anouk, an old acquaintance of Jerry. Now she is married to a rich businessman: her kidnappers have demanded a large ransom. It won’t be easy for our men to free her and return home alive…
name: Mister No 300: Sotto il Segno dell'Avventura

description: Mister No is on holiday in Rio with his friend Patricia. He sees an old acquaintance, Doctor Sandy Wang, whom he met during the war when she was just a girl. Mister No is overcome with a wave of memories. He tells Patricia about the time when, in ’42, he was sent to Guadalcanal. There he found Alan Chambers again, whom he already knew, and the tough Steve Malloy and Phil Mulligan, although in the beginning he didn’t like the latter. But then, during a difficult mission he changed his mind about him…
name: Guadalcanal!

description: Guadalcanal,1942. There is a suicide mission for Mister No, Phil Mulligan, Alan Chambers and Steve Mallory. They have to infiltrate the Japanese lines, in the jungle, and recover an important secret services officer who has fallen into the hands of the enemy, Colonel Stark!
name: Una Stagione all'Inferno

description: Colonel Stark involves Mister No and his comrades in a “mission impossible”: to find professor Leon Kaplan, physicist of international fame, who is hiding on a Pacific Island after having interrupted his studies on a new powerful bomb. But the Japanese are also looking for him …
name: Sulle Tracce di Mister Kaplan

description: The Molengaos are a tribe of Indios who are very special: because of a hereditary genetic defect, they see in black and white and feel comfortable only in the dark. Mister No guides an expedition of anthropologists who want to study them. But someone else is following them: relentless mercenaries who want to lay their hands on the emerald-mines hidden within the territories of the tribe!
name: Occhi Nelle Tenebre

description: Anna Ripley is a United States journalist who has arrived at Manaus to … interview Mister No ! But she ends up in the same trouble Jerry is involved in, when our pilot accepts to transport a cargo over the jungle. Its owner, Alejandro Cortenez , wants in fact to get rid of a hot load and does not hesitate to sabotage the aeroplane so that it will fall in an unexplored territory.
name: Sull'Orlo dell'Abisso

description: Surviving an aerial disaster, Mister No and Anna Ripley must now cross an unexplored territory in order to return to “civilization”. There however, live the Maku, indios braves to whom every white man is an enemy. To help the two dispersed arrive Esse-Esse and Jesus, a young Indian who guides them.
name: La Notte del Sacrificio

description: Juanito, the Indian rebel who Mister No had convinced to surrender after his tribe had risked being exterminated, escapes from prison in order to rejoin his family. In the reserve, however, a group of Garimpeiros have caused a massacre. And now the rage of Juanito cannot be stopped…
name: Juanito il Ribelle
